'''禍水妞圖像'''（Jailbait images）是指外貌符合[[禍水妞|禍水妞]]定義的[[最低合法性行為年齡|未成年人]]的[[性化|性化]]圖像。禍水妞圖像跟一般[[兒童色情|兒童色情]]的區別在於前者「通常不會包含裸體」<ref name=boost/><ref name=pcmag/>。它們主要拍攝[[前青少年期|前青少年期]]或青少年早期的少女身穿輕薄衣物（比如[[比基尼泳衣|比基尼泳衣]]、短裙、[[内衣|内衣]]）的樣子<ref name=gawk>{{cite news|last=Chen |first=Adrian |title=Unmasking Reddit's Violentacrez, The Biggest Troll on the Web |url=http://gawker.com/5950981/unmasking-reddits-violentacrez-the-biggest-troll-on-the-web |accessdate=2014-06-12 |newspaper=Gawker |date=2012-10-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121012213707/http://gawker.com/5950981/unmasking-reddits-violentacrez-the-biggest-troll-on-the-web |archivedate=2012-10-12 }}</ref><ref name=pcmag>{{cite web |url=https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2391317,00.asp |title=Reddit Closes 'Jailbait' Pic Site, Allows Others to Remain |last1=Hachman |first1=Mark |date=2011-08-10 |work=[[PC_Magazine|PC Magazine]] |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-12 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003012639/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2391317,00.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

禍水妞圖像在道德或法律上具有爭議性。有關圖像或搜尋字眼皆曾遭到審查。

==法律與審查==
禍水妞圖像的法律地位備受爭議。法律分析師{{link-en|杰弗里·托宾|Jeffrey Toobin}}認為它們在美國是合法的。法律專家{{link-en|珊妮·霍斯汀|Sunny Hostin}}則持懷疑態度，認為禍水妞圖像的尺度落在兒童色情的「边缘」，因此可能是違法的<ref name=mediaite>{{cite web |url=http://www.mediaite.com/tv/anderson-cooper-excoriates-reddit-for-creepy-jailbait-section/ |title=Anderson Cooper Excoriates Reddit For ‘Creepy’ Jailbait Section |last1=Crugnale |first1=James |date=2011-09-30 |work=Mediaite |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-12 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325034525/https://www.mediaite.com/tv/anderson-cooper-excoriates-reddit-for-creepy-jailbait-section/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2012/10/18/us/internet-troll-apology/ |title=Man behind 'Jailbait' posts exposed, loses job |last1=Fitzpatrick |first1=David |last2=Griffin |first2=Drew |date=2012-10-19 |work=[[有线电视新闻网|CNN]] |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-12 |archive-date=2021-03-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210302181408/https://edition.cnn.com/2012/10/18/us/internet-troll-apology/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。儘管禍水妞圖像在美國可能是合法的，但大眾一般認為它們「意識不良」<ref name=mediaite /><ref name=shutdown />。[[Instagram|Instagram]]和[[Tumblr|Tumblr]]皆禁止用戶以禍水妞作[[主題標籤|主題標籤]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/29/banned-instagram-hashtags_n_4171589.html |title=The New Banned Hashtags Of Instagram -- Now With More #SexyTimes |last1=Bosker |first1=Biance |date=2013-10-29 |work=[[赫芬顿邮报|The Huffington Post]] |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019082747/https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/10/29/banned-instagram-hashtags_n_4171589.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://thedatapack.com/banned-hashtags-instagram/ |title=The Banned #Hashtags of Instagram |date=2013-08-26 |work=thedatapack.com |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714205237/http://thedatapack.com/banned-hashtags-instagram/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailydot.com/business/banned-tumblr-tags-mobile/ |title=29 tags Tumblr banned from its mobile app (and 10 it didn't) |last1=Romano |first1=Aja |date=2013-06-18 |publisher=The Daily Dot |website=DailyDot.com |accessdate=014-07-19 |archive-date=2021-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325124639/https://www.dailydot.com/business/banned-tumblr-tags-mobile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Google搜索|Google搜索建議]]亦不會向用戶返回此一字詞<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.2600.com/googleblacklist/ |title=Google Blacklist – Words That Google Instant Doesn't Like |magazine=2600: The Hacker Quarterly |accessdate=2014-06-19 |journal= |archive-date=2017-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110023530/https://www.2600.com/googleblacklist/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。禍水妞圖像的辯護者曾以[[言論自由|言論自由]]和打入主流的未成年人性化映像（比如[[布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯|布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯]]為《[[爱的初告白_(歌曲)|爱的初告白]]》錄下的音樂錄像）作辯護理據<ref name=AlfonsoIII>{{cite news|last=Alfonso III|first=Fernando|title=A free-speech haven wrestles with violent images|url=http://www.dailydot.com/society/reddit-beatingwomen-misogyny-images/|accessdate=2014-06-12|newspaper=The Daily Dot|date=2011-08-11|archive-date=2013-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130112220640/http://www.dailydot.com/society/reddit-beatingwomen-misogyny-images/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=gawk />。

==線上流傳==
人們常在少女的[[Facebook|Facebook]]頁面收集其上傳的禍水妞圖像<ref name=ban>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailydot.com/news/reddit-ban-jailbait-international/ |title=Reddit's ban on r/jailbait goes international |last1=Morris |first1=Kevin |date=2011-08-23 |newspaper=The Daily Dot |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-12 |archive-date=2018-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181203210238/https://www.dailydot.com/news/reddit-ban-jailbait-international/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分網頁和論壇專為禍水妞圖像收集者而設。除了上传和分享图片，禍水妞圈子還會討論[[戀青少年|戀青少年]]、戀青少年與[[恋童|恋童]]的區別、某名少女是否年幼或成熟得不能歸類為「禍水妞」<ref name=jezebel/>。《[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]]》雜誌評論道，大多媒體在[[阿曼达·陶德自杀事件|阿曼达·陶德自杀事件]]中忽略了禍水妞圖像討論版所扮演的角色<ref name=destroy />。某個被指在陶德自杀前骚扰她的嫌疑人，有在禍水妞論壇上發文和圖片。該篇文章還形容禍水妞論壇是「互联网上一股非常隐蔽的力量，在當中可以發現过于聪明的恋童者對缺乏安全感的青少年進行『坑蒙拐骗』」<ref name=destroy>{{cite web |url=https://www.vice.com/read/a-jailbait-loving-perv-destroyed-amanda-todds-life |title=A Jailbait Loving Perv Destroyed Amanda Todd's Life |last1=McGuire |first1=Patrick |date=2012-10-15 |work=[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]] |publisher= |accessdate=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2016-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160428233845/http://www.vice.com/read/a-jailbait-loving-perv-destroyed-amanda-todds-life |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外也有報導表示「它們提供了一道窗口，讓人們一探一些令人不安的想法」<ref name=jezebel>{{cite web |url=http://jezebel.com/5842172/reddits-pedophilia-defenders-and-the-return-of-jailbait |title=Reddit's Pedophilia Posse And The Return Of Jailbait |last1=North |first1=Anna |date=2011-09-20 |publisher=Jezebel |website=Jezebel.com |accessdate=2014-16-19 |archive-date=2018-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519120040/https://jezebel.com/5842172/reddits-pedophilia-defenders-and-the-return-of-jailbait |dead-url=no }}</ref>。部分禍水妞社群成員自稱為恋童者<ref name=jezebel />。

===Reddit爭議===
[[Reddit|Reddit]]的分版/r/jailbait曾是較具知名度的禍水妞圈子。人們在[[Google|Google]]搜尋「jailbait」時，第一個結果就是這個分版<ref name=pcmag />。它一度成為把用戶導向至Reddit的第二大字眼，僅次於「Reddit」一詞<ref name=gawk />。

2011年9月29日，[[安德森·库珀|安德森·库珀]]在其电视节目中花了一段时间谴责该分版和容許该分版存在的Reddit，使其受到广泛关注<ref name=boost>{{cite news |last=Morris |first=Kevin |title=Anderson Cooper addresses Reddit's teen pics section |url=http://www.dailydot.com/news/anderson-cooper-jailbait-reddit/ |newspaper=The Daily Dot |date= 2011-09-30 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20140621064927/http://www.dailydot.com/news/anderson-cooper-jailbait-reddit/ |archivedate=2014-06-21 |deadurl=no|access-date= 2014-06-28 }}</ref>。2011年10月10日，该分版被Reddit管理員关闭<ref name=shutdown>{{cite news|last=Morris|first=Kevin|title=Reddit shuts down r/jailbait|url=http://www.dailydot.com/society/reddit-r-jailbait-shutdown-controversy/|accessdate=2014-06-12|newspaper=The Daily Dot|date=2011-10-11|archive-date=2013-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130926122135/http://www.dailydot.com/society/reddit-r-jailbait-shutdown-controversy/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

